      72.38,
      392.8,
      447.04,
      423.36
    ],
    "text": "Read the following instructions on \u2018how to write a formal letter\u2019. Write them in your book in the proper order.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.38,
      429.0,
      427.95,
      553.36
    ],
    "text": "A. Use an appropriate salutation to the person you are writing to.B. Write the sender\u2019s address on the top left hand side of the page.C. Sign off your letter with an appropriate closing.D. Place the recipient\u2019s designation and address one line beneath the date.E. Write the body of the letter.F. Write the subject of the letter and underline it.G. Place the date directly below the sender's address.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
