      172.26,
      177.23,
      350.57,
      279.99
    ],
    "text": "NOTICEA Shramadana Campaign will be held on 30th May 2015 from 7.30 a.m. to 1.30 p.m. to clean Danpitiya Tank bund and the Children\u2019s Park. Refreshments and a complementary cap will be provided. All are invited.",
