    "text": "A woman entered a shop and saw a little dog. He asked the shopkeeper \"Does your dog bite?\"The shopkeeper said, \"No, my dog does not bite.\"The woman tried to pet the dog and the dog bit her.\"Ouch!\" She exclaimed, \u201cDidn\u2019t you say your dog doesn\u2019t bite?\"The shopkeeper replied, \"That is not my dog!\"",
